data.description: 4.41 acres in Haralson county! This modern farmhouse has 3BR/2BA, includes a large open kitchen with a view of family room, plenty of cabinets, electric stove, breakfast bar and dining area, spiral staircase to the loft bedroom, on the porch there is entertainment center for you to watch you favorite sports teams, all hardwood and tile flooring, the out building also has it's on power meter.  So come and relax under the covered front porch, or enjoy a quiet evening on the back deck over looking your pool.
